  <h2>Treasure Chest Rewards</h2>

  <p>When you clear the dungeon, you are given a variety of rewards. These include consumables, two lower head gear, and items that can be used to craft memorial dungeon equipment.</p>

  <p>If there are more members in your party, more reward items will drop.</p>

  <h3>Consumables</h3>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-4">
    <li>Red Potion</li>
    <li>Blue Potion</li>
    <li>Orange Potion</li>
    <li>Yellow Potion</li>
    <li>White Potion</li>
    <li>Green Potion</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Lower headgear</h3>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-4">
    <li>Wearable by all classes.</li>
    <li>No slot.</li>
    <li>Your character must be at least base level 30 to wear this headgear.</li>
    <li>Can be enchanted.</li>
    <li>Weight: 10</li>
    <li>Increase your movement speed while transformed. This does not stack with Increase Agility.</li>
  </ul>

